----------------------------------------------------------------

I hope you guys enjoy the map, I definitely learned a lot making this one. Pretty much been working on this 6-8 hours a day constantly for the past month and a half. This was the most hellish process I've gone through making a map (pretty much almost everything kept going wrong) but I think it turned out well and by far is the best map I've produced to date.

If there are any issues with the map, feel free to contact me on discord: PrisonNightmare#7061
